    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-floor luster. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, free of stone chips or swirl marks, and protected by a high-grade ceramic coating that makes the deep metallic finish pop. Inside, the cabin remains in time-capsule condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or tactile imperfections. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a full binder of service documentation from authorized specialists, ensuring that every fluid flush and inspection was performed ahead of schedule. There are no leaks, no rattles, and the engine delivers smooth, effortless power. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for someone who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
